sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Používateľ
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Backend API
    participant ORD as Order Service
    participant PAY as Payment Gateway
    participant DB as Database
    participant MAIL as Email Service

    User->>FE: Klikne Kúpiť
    FE->>API: POST /orders
    API->>ORD: createOrder()
    ORD->>DB: uloženie objednávky
    ORD->>PAY: autorizácia platby
    PAY-->>ORD: výsledok platby
    ORD->>MAIL: potvrdenie objednávky
    API-->>FE: 201 Created
    FE-->>User: Zobrazenie potvrdenia
